name: LooksLikeGame
0:

”Alexa, tell the looks like game to play something from this year.”

skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: looks like game
des:
Listen to a random "Looks Like" selection provided by listeners to ESPN's Dan Lebatard Show with Stugotz. The selection will also be displayed in the Alexa app.

There are currently over 200 sayings. Looks like sayings will be updated periodically.

(Tree Frog Labs has no affiliation with ESPN or the Dan Le Batard Show with Stugotz. Content used in the skill is public domain content contributed to the show by its listeners and is freely available from numerous sources on the internet.)
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
